<rdg source="bib:Hultzsch1900-1901_06">mahātagi-varena</rdg>
<note>Vogel (<bibl rend="omitname"><ptr target="bib:Vogel1929-1930_01"/><citedRange unit="page">7</citedRange><citedRange unit="note">1</citedRange></bibl>) saw that <foreign>mahā-talavarena</foreign> is expected here, but imagined a scribal error. The shape of <foreign>la</foreign> is eccentric only at first sight, but regular for this hand. See, e.g., <foreign>br̥hatphalāyana</foreign> in line 7. See also <bibl><ptr target="bib:NilakantaSastri+Gopalachari1937-1938_01"/></bibl>.</note>
